{"tid":2238981,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"細心諗返轉頭，以前有啲中學同學窮得好誇張","createTime":"2020-10-11T14:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T08:40:12.000Z","uid":41524,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b8af4e3b551e1c34233c680e5f3357a5dba82a","tid":2238981,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"嗰陣冇好深入咁諗<br />\n只知佢哋係窮人<br />\n但有啲事係幾離譜吓，究竟佢哋嘅父母點解可以廢成咁<br />\n<br />\n1.書包都冇錢買，要係街執或者問同學借舊書包嚟用（其實當送俾佢）<br />\n<br />\n2.冇錢食飯，問同學分俾佢食，唔介意食人哋食剩嗰啲，食人口水尾<br />\n<br />\n3.打機要用幾十蚊買隻game入面啲嘢，儲一個月零用錢<br />\n<br />\n4.有個女同學一星期只有100蚊飯錢，但佢個人都幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都真係幾癲"},{"pid":"1c7893e7d8605f199e0ac507caeb637abb8bbd64","tid":2238981,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而加仲係"},{"pid":"15ac0bc67641ddd7b53e5ee079adaa5ddde49777","tid":2238981,"uid":42064,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"4.有個女同學一星期只有100蚊飯錢，但佢個人都幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮，本身唔瘦底，食杯麵食m記唔通會瘦"},{"pid":"53d1b1a1c6f4e98fe3bd11ba0f835922aee5f457","tid":2238981,"uid":78302,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"一個禮拜一舊, 每日廿蚊, 真係淨係食到撈麵同麵包<br />\n諗起細個都有D同學唔知係因為窮定點, 為左慳錢<br />\n日日淨係魚蛋燒賣當lunch, 一係啪個小食部濕鳩撈麵就算, 通常都係瘦撚矮撚<br />\n但同時又會有D私樓女同學為左減肥lunch食粒糖就算, 屋企十鳩幾樓行樓梯, 最後暈撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界真係好撚奇怪"},{"pid":"03e52473aa16ed614944810e3f2dd81b4aff7f5f","tid":2238981,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"15ac0bc67641ddd7b53e5ee079adaa5ddde49777","tid":2238981,"uid":42064,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"4.有個女同學一星期只有100蚊飯錢，但佢個人都幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮，本身唔瘦底，食杯麵食m記唔通會瘦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:15:45.000Z","msg":"十年前夠食啦."},{"pid":"21a84d4733f4518f20becec6e4f9602acd980a68","tid":2238981,"uid":191633,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"十年前 學校飯盒14蚊個"},{"pid":"e832cc2dc358493b7d1ca0c4ad56351a34d6fb42","tid":2238981,"uid":351453,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"21a84d4733f4518f20becec6e4f9602acd980a68","tid":2238981,"uid":191633,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"十年前 學校飯盒14蚊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"總會有啲濕鳩街市有燒味飯盒賣<br />\n試過有個同學想儲錢買禮物去溝女 成班兄弟陪佢一齊捱撈麵捱飯盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果我地其他人儲得仲多過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a7d3887c7f0bb14430c06895054d2adbffa543","tid":2238981,"uid":2590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"581927a32f8c6764dd9f8732a7da09e8ce1e1c81","tid":2238981,"uid":341040,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"00年初 100絕對夠食到肥肥白白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1236328f78712e88b3ed2af44666bc9311cc162","tid":2238981,"uid":299360,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"15ac0bc67641ddd7b53e5ee079adaa5ddde49777","tid":2238981,"uid":42064,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"4.有個女同學一星期只有100蚊飯錢，但佢個人都幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮，本身唔瘦底，食杯麵食m記唔通會瘦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"唔好笑人 窮人易肥過有錢人 垃圾食物又唔健康又肥"},{"pid":"3c05c8c6a6a2cd31d26dbd3e2f353382ff75d345","tid":2238981,"uid":184388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"以前好似有個小學同學係着校服當睡衣"},{"pid":"5078da90f3edddf2e5409d58f5594b9b440e50da","tid":2238981,"uid":42064,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f1236328f78712e88b3ed2af44666bc9311cc162","tid":2238981,"uid":299360,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"15ac0bc67641ddd7b53e5ee079adaa5ddde49777","tid":2238981,"uid":42064,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"4.有個女同學一星期只有100蚊飯錢，但佢個人都幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮，本身唔瘦底，食杯麵食m記唔通會瘦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"唔好笑人 窮人易肥過有錢人 垃圾食物又唔健康又肥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"我咪講緊同一樣嘢"},{"pid":"9db8fa29bcfce79a11992ccd6433bfb582f71d48","tid":2238981,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c05c8c6a6a2cd31d26dbd3e2f353382ff75d345","tid":2238981,"uid":184388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"以前好似有個小學同學係着校服當睡衣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"關窮唔窮事咩"},{"pid":"5ad68bcfa6ade6eff9e524ecb64019c56bd16ef6","tid":2238981,"uid":37389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9db8fa29bcfce79a11992ccd6433bfb582f71d48","tid":2238981,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c05c8c6a6a2cd31d26dbd3e2f353382ff75d3